						               													<description>E ADESSO?!/AND NOW?! is an economic-oriented game inspired to Role-Playing Games, what future awaits an old sorcerer, fighter, paladin etc. after their retirement?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How they invest their gold pieces and how they maintain their glory and fame?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In E ADESSO?!/AND NOW?! 3-6 players are ex-adventures whose, once retired, are trying to invest their gold, trying go to become more and more famous and to climb social hierarchy and now, becoming older, they need the services of young adventures.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To reach their targets now they must buy land, build manors, trying to attract people and build a little village, engage young adventurers to defend their proprieties, and defend themselves from any kind of bureaucracy, an hard work, the main challenge must still start&amp;hellip;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game includes:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Easy to understand Rules&amp;#10;    Map of a city and surrounding area&amp;#10;    Counters including gold, adventures, manors and more.&amp;#10;    Charts and tables for easy play.&amp;#10;    The game system is based on &amp;ldquo;Metropolis&amp;rdquo; (Editoy) game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Actually the game is in Italian only.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is totally free and all files needed to print &amp;amp; play are included here.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Designer     Gian Carlo Porciani&amp;#10;Artist             Gian Carlo Porciani&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
